OL,5, A former NHS chief executive is suing  
OL,6, her employer, saying she was "bullied, 
OL,7, harassed, intimidated and undermined"  
OL,8, by the hospital trust's chairman.      
OL,10,FIn legal papers, seen by BBC News, Dr  
OL,11,FSusan Gilby alleges she was effectively
OL,12,Funfairly dismissed by the Countess of  
OL,13,FChester NHS Foundation Trust, after she
OL,14,Fmade a formal complaint.               
OL,16,FShe has also accused the chairman of   
OL,17,Fputting finance above patient safety.  
OL,19,FIn a statement, the trust said it      
OL,20,Fdenied all the allegations.            
